title: Coffee Evolution
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Independent coffee shop with a welcoming vibe. Offers panini, salad, bagels and drinks. Offers a salad bowl of roast veg, chickpeas, salad greens, olives, toast, humus, oil and balsamic dressing. Or you could get bagel with humus and roast veg. Non-dairy milks for drinks.
